{"tid":758334,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[Siri 開鏡直播] 封閉的惡夢 closed nightmare","createTime":"2018-07-27T14:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T17:58:39.000Z","uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dae59a7cd1985fe82dcb543ea25fdd5312aa2220","tid":758334,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232508_b4ab4875e473e3d1f44475ba8ab5253d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232508_b4ab4875e473e3d1f44475ba8ab5253d.png&h=769b8431&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232511_c0fd401055fe2054ffe9ef3064a4d538.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232511_c0fd401055fe2054ffe9ef3064a4d538.png&h=a2be16d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.twitch.tv%2Fsirihoihoi&d=Dof9DDvoUSP8Q9BL3XsNpNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f63f9b30\" target=\"_blank\">https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">台已開～一齊入黎玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n劇場型恐怖冒險遊戲《CLOSED NIGHTMARE 封閉的惡夢》是結合了寫實影像與冒險遊戲的全新恐怖娛樂。最大的特徵是使用寫實影像的呈現方式，事件場景以能夠體驗主角看見的場景的第一人稱視角影片進行。<br />\n<br />\n　　玩家是在一片陰暗且什麼都沒有的房間醒來之喪失記憶的女性。在混亂之中突然響起的電話中傳來小孩的聲音......。「妳是上代真莉亞，本實驗的參加者。」、「妳要負責進行某個任務。」。 在一無所知的情形下，真莉亞只能往前邁進。儘管此時的她完全不知道，接下來將要面對無數不可理喻的恐怖――<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232937_16d34f210a6d9968c389a47671bc1770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232937_16d34f210a6d9968c389a47671bc1770.png&h=7e917307&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232938_11dfdb01cb16ab31b265977957217f2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232938_11dfdb01cb16ab31b265977957217f2d.png&h=43008a13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43b125b4b23371908c1cea837e1e2493c2967d0a","tid":758334,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4632cb3b115b37c80a7f1b11ec06b270153de3","tid":758334,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b320d9e3b6644cf30fedf371bbc233087b053af","tid":758334,"uid":141240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab4cdfc434f6fd301b4fa9c0d1021437775fbf6","tid":758334,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a621b0f8aeec07e8e8730f898dc087b28f10645","tid":758334,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore